Subject: {{collective.name}} would love to be hosted by {{host.name}}

{{> header}}

<div class="hidden">Request submitted by {{user.collective.name}}</div>

<h1>{{collective.name}}</h1>

<style>
  th {
    text-align: left;
  }
</style>

Dear admin of {{host.name}},

<p>
  {{user.collective.name}} would love you to host their {{collective.name}} collective.
</p>

<p>By hosting them, you accept to collect money on their behalf and account for all of their transactions in your
  books. For that service you will receive a commission of {{host.hostFeePercent}}% on all their donations (you
  can edit that commission in the settings of your host on <a
    href="https://opencollective.com/{{host.slug}}/edit">https://opencollective.com/{{host.slug}}/edit</a>.
  You can read more about what it entails to be a host in our <a
    href="https://docs.opencollective.com/help/hosts">FAQ</a>.</p>

<h2>Collective details</h2>
<table>
  <tr>
    <th>Name</th>
    <td>{{collective.name}}</td>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <th>Url</th>
    <td><a href="https://opencollective.com/{{collective.slug}}">https://opencollective.com/{{collective.slug}}</a></td>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <th>Website</th>
    <td>{{collective.website}}</td>
  </tr>
  {{#if collective.data.meetupSlug}}
  <tr>
    <th>Meetup</th>
    <td>https://meetup.com/{{collective.data.meetupSlug}}</td>
  </tr>
  {{/if}}
  {{#if collective.data.members}}
  <tr>
    <th>Members</th>
    <td>{{collective.data.members}}</td>
  </tr>
  {{/if}}
  <tr>
    <th>Twitter</th>
    <td>{{collective.twitterHandle}}</td>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <th>Description</th>
    <td>{{collective.description}}</td>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <th>Tags</th>
    <td>{{{json collective.tags}}}</td>
  </tr>
</table>

<h2>Creator</h2>
https://opencollective.com/{{user.collective.slug}}
<br /><br />
<table>
  <tr>
    <th>Name</th>
    <td>{{user.collective.name}}</td>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <th>Email</th>
    <td>{{user.email}}</td>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <th>Website</th>
    <td>{{user.collective.website}}</td>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <th>Twitter</th>
    <td>{{user.collective.twitterHandle}}</td>
  </tr>
</table>

<br /><br />
<center>
  <a href="{{actions.approve}}" class="btn blue">
    <div>APPROVE</div>
  </a>
</center>

{{> footer}}